{"tid":680644,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"香港樓市?!地表裂縫現詭異「藍火」 恐發生大爆炸","createTime":"2018-05-27T10:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T11:39:25.000Z","uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d769056f244d3ba64fe652734fb3bb637726b737","tid":680644,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T10:39:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180526/58236306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180526%2F58236306&d=JLNiTcM%2FumB9ObWVpLrhmp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=09dd8778\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180526%2F58236306&h=16e0f9c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180526/58236306</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美國夏威夷島的基拉韋厄火山（Kilauea Volcano）月初爆發，熾熱的熔岩流經森林和行人路，科學家在現場觀察到地表的裂縫中冒出藍色火焰。<br />\n<br />\n這些「藍火」之所以出現，是因為火山產生的地底甲烷氣體透過地表裂縫逸出，再被燃燒的熔岩點燃。美國地質勘探局科學家<br />\n形容：「這非常戲劇化，同時又非常可怕」。<br />\n火山產生的甲烷對夏威夷島居民構成重大威脅，如果甲烷在地底被點燃的話，可以引發大爆炸。<br />\n火山爆發令夏威夷地表多處出現巨大裂縫，有一個家庭周一在疏散後回家執拾物件，驚見家園底下有一條闊6至7米的巨型裂縫，恐引起地陷，吞噬整間屋。<br />\n火山爆發至今已經過了3星期，熔岩不斷湧出、火山灰大噴發，地震亦時有發生。夏威夷當局下令約2,000人疏散，而<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">被熔岩摧毀的建築物</span>增至82幢。"},{"pid":"d33909d4b524563d5739ca38ca93585a31ea3295","tid":680644,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T10:40:43.000Z","msg":"發展商：又有多d新地起新樓"},{"pid":"2531a676ff91cb5cbb9d56930dac4bd0d6efa5e0","tid":680